  <prefercite id="aspace_f1d2db8ae8a987bcebf3c52c0b9e1880">
    <head>Cite As:</head>
<p>The New York State Veterinary Medical Society Auxiliary records, #6600. Division of Rare and Manuscript Collections, Cornell University Library.</p>  </prefercite>
  <scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_f8e8caa24602aa6f7d52d6806e0f9f50">
    <head>Scope and content</head>
<p>Scrapbooks and subject files kept by the New York State Veterinary Medical Society Auxiliary from 1948-2000. Also, files relating to annual meetings, awards sponsored by the Auxiliary, and State Fair displays.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_d7575d7ec1d6eb641ea6cf23877fcc52">
    <head>Scope and content</head>
<p>Includes reports, correspondence and financial files.</p>  </scopecontent>
